      "text": "You\u2019re better off dying a terrorist than dying as a Trump supporter when it comes to legacy media coverage.\n\n\nVariety (@Variety)\n\nChuck Norris Was a Great Action Star -- but Politics May Overshadow His Legacy variety.com/2026/film/opinio\u2026\n\n\n\n\n\u2014 https://nitter.net/Variety/status/2035075441216655607#m",
