    {
      "voiceId": "clay-travis",
      "voiceName": "Clay Travis",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "This is going to continue to grow. Blue states are going to lose their wealthiest residents to red states. That will make red states even better and blue states even worse. Which will lead to the cycle accelerating.\n\n\nStephen Moore (@StephenMoore)\n\nNew IRS domestic migration data shows tens of billions of dollars continuing to move into low-tax states.\u00a0\n\nFrom 2022 to 2023, the largest net income gains came at the expense of high-tax states losing residents, income, and opportunity.\u00a0\n\nAmericans a",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/ClayTravis/status/2035061640979222537",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-20T18:31:19+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
